user.biography:
Official Page of Montauk Brewing Company + Montauk Hard Seltzer - Must be 21+ to follow.
“Come As You Are”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of cloud, nature and ocean.

node.text: Fun things are on the horizon - stay tuned. There’s things like new Ocean Series limited releases, a local Blueberry Ale, Montauk Pumpkin Ale returns and so much more. Have a nice little Tuesday! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company.

node.text: Head over to our online store for old favorites and new hits. Looks like this season’s top seller is the crew neck sweatshirt. Super soft, extra cozy and perfect for those summer nights! Link in bio. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Stock up on all the necessities including ice cold @montaukbrewco ahead of the storm! The taproom will be closed tomorrow out of an abundance of caution for our team and fans. Believe us, the dog isn’t pumped about this storm either. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of twilight, cloud, nature and ocean.

node.text: Good morning, from Montauk. Happy Friday everyone. Now let’s have a day and celebrate with some @montaukbrewco later on! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Beach Break Double IPA is being canned fresh right this moment and will be available at noon. Grab your 4 pack and limited edition Beach Break tank top while supplies last! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Union Square Park. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Montauk Summer Ale is a great choice for all summer occasions, it could be THE choice for all summer occasions. Maybe you enjoy your @montaukbrewco on the beach, at the pool, backyard BBQ, rooftop or city stoop. Wherever that might be, THANK YOU for celebrating with Montauk Brewing Company and stay tuned for upcoming fall and winter news! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on August 16, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: The summer heat is upon us and there’s no better way to stay cool than with an ice cold Watermelon Session. Grab a six pack while you still can because this beer will be gone from shelves very soon! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company.

node.text: This year Montauk Brewing Company turned 9. We released a limited edition can with @surfridereasternlongisland and had a custom surfboard shaped by @faktionsurfboards - fans came from all over and signed this board and now it lives in the taproom. Thank you to all of our awesome fans for your incredible support. Also, THANK YOU to our amazing team for your hard work and passion for bringing more @montaukbrewco to more people each and every day! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Navy Road. May be an image of body of water.

node.text: A few minutes ago in Montauk, the sun set in spectacular fashion and a lot of people were on the beach taking pictures and enjoying @montaukbrewco beers. The dog didn’t seem to notice. Hope everyone has a nice little Saturday night! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Hopefully this is your current situation. Stay cool, friends. #montauk #comeasyouare 📸 @jamesmorano

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company.

node.text: Here’s a sneak peek at the newest six pack in our year round lineup arriving in a few short weeks! We’ve been working on the recipe for a couple of years and thanks to a lot of fan feedback, we think we got it right where you want it. Easy Riser Belgian White is mellow and easy going, like a gently rising wave as it approaches the shore. Brewed with coriander and orange peel, Easy Riser is incredibly smooth and, as the name suggests, incredibly easy to love. Stay tuned for news on the launch! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company with @jjamet, @creich910, @breich84, and @montaukcyclecompany. May be an image of one or more people, people riding bicycles, people standing, bicycle and road.

node.text: A couple of years ago we started this thing called Hot Laps where a few friends would meet up at the brewery every Thursday around 5:15PM, race a few miles around a loop in Montauk as fast as possible and then finish with a celebratory pint @montaukbrewco - It’s unsanctioned and quite dangerous, it’s like Fight Club but instead of not talking about it, we talk about it with anyone who will listen. Maybe we should look into making this a sanctioned thing, just maybe. #montauk #comeasyouare
